  "texts": [
    "Additionally, being familiar with the motor themes offers valuable insights into the field's primary challenges and prospects, assisting researchers in developing new research questions and hypotheses.",
    "Evolution of social network anonymization themesAfter examining how the number of common keywords changes throughout various subperiods.",
    "Subsequently, we investigated the development of thematic areas to track the progression of themes.As depicted in Fig. 25, there is a variation in the constancy of keywords across each subperiod.",
    "Although several keywords consistently appear, some newly appear or fade away within each subperiod.",
    "In addition, specific keywords like \"T-closeness\" exhibit uniqueness by being exclusive to particular subperiods."
